    <h3> Masquerade as an Instructor </h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Find the instructor's <a href="#find-netid" data-toggle="tab">netid</a></li>
      <li>Go to <a href="https://reserves.library.nd.edu">https://reserves.library.nd.edu</a>.</li>
      <li>Select Masqurade from the top navigation.</li>
      <li>Enter the netid in the Netid: box and press "Go". </li>
      <li>There should now be orange text on the top right indicating you are masquerading as your instructor.</li>
      <li>Do your tasks.<li>
      <li>When you are done select the orande text, "Stop Masquerading as .....", to go back to your user acount.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>


  <div class="tab-pane" id="find-netid">
    <h3> Find a Netid </h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Go to: <a href="https://apps.nd.edu/webdirectory/directory.cfm">https://apps.nd.edu/webdirectory/directory.cfm</a></li>
      <li>Search for the person you want to login as</li>
      <li>Select their name from the list</li>
      <li>Click on More Info (underneath "View personal web page.")</li>
      <li>The net id is the field labled "uid" in the right column.</li>
      <li>Hightlight it and hit control - c to copy.</li>
    </ol>

